```

3. Create a function to find the nth Fibonacci number using recursion:

```cpp
int fibonacci_nth(int n, Fibonacci fibonacci) {
    if (n <= 0)
        return 0;
    if (n == 1)
        return 1;
    return fibonacci[n - 1] + fibonacci[n - 2];
}
```

4. Write the main function to call the recursive function and print the result:

```cpp
